_sText:
Map from M.I.A. Jailbreak. I have multiple versions but this is the most recent one.

Blackops is one of the most iconic Jailbreak maps that spans across multiple games. It was created in late 2008 for the Jailbreak server M.I.A. 24/7 Jailbreak and actually caused a lot of drama about how much each creator contributed to Blackops, with M.I.A. insisting that the map wouldn't exist without his help.

Â The map was named after Blackops, which according to M.I.A. was so he could he could show his appreciation for him.
